<div class="fav_bar">
<span class="fav_bar-label">View as:</span>
<a href="#" onclick="javascript:window.print();" class="fav_print" title="Print">Print</a>
<a href="/about-communications/mobile-apps/" class="mobile-apps" title="MOBILE APPS">Mobile App</a>
